title: Loyal Divide - Labrador EP
description:
Loyal Divide is an up-and-coming Electronic Indie band based in Chicago, IL. Their new Labrador EP is exemplary of their genre-fusing music and is the result of many months of basement sessions. Slaves to their passion they play as though every song were their last - the kind of drive born from one too many nine to fives. Make sure you pick this up.

*NOTE* This is an official band-sponsored torrent and is 100% legal to download and share. Get the word out.
